  "3034650": {
    "name": "BloomKeeper",
    "steam_appid": 3034650,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/eb68f6b03512739c2892df46fae5e99b.poster.avif?t=1770910965\" width=1170 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/eb68f6b03512739c2892df46fae5e99b.webm?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/eb68f6b03512739c2892df46fae5e99b.mp4?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >让世界重焕生机</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界一片焦土，皮克一如既往地苏醒，修复这片满目疮痍的环境。但面对如此巨大的灾难，这些天真好奇的小家伙们需要你的帮助和指引；你就是它们的守护者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引导他们，保护他们免受环境侵害，但最重要的是保护他们免受自身伤害；由于他们意识不到危险，你需要及时采取行动，将他们引向毁灭的源头。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >携手共创自然新生。每一粒种子种下后，都能帮助生命再次绽放，但务必保持警惕，烧毁的区域永无止境地扩张。若想抵达这片焦土的源头，就必须策略性地种植植被。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/13afaefa53940e92bd92cdaf985ccfb0.poster.avif?t=1770910965\" width=1170 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/13afaefa53940e92bd92cdaf985ccfb0.webm?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/13afaefa53940e92bd92cdaf985ccfb0.mp4?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >引导你的皮克羊群</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你种的皮库斯越多，得到的皮克就越多！把它们聚集起来，一路种植到你的目标地点，不要让它们散开。在兽群两侧围成一团移动，保持兽群紧凑，这样你就能高效地推进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你离下一个皮库斯还差几米吗？扔个皮克吧！轻巧圆润，总能精准地击中你的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你最大的敌人？悬崖、湖泊，以及对皮克聚集最大的威胁：蝴蝶！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/c8714343972e237c59813120654770c4.poster.avif?t=1770910965\" width=1170 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/c8714343972e237c59813120654770c4.webm?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/c8714343972e237c59813120654770c4.mp4?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >防止烧伤区域扩散</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为皮克的守护者，你必须以战略和智慧引导他们。焦土将不断扩张，直到其源头得到平息。只有悬崖峭壁才能阻止这些区域的扩张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带着你的皮克到达其他皮库斯，但最重要的是，不要失去他们！否则，可怕的恶皮克就会出现……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >离焦土源头越近，焦土蔓延速度就越快。务必重新造林，确保整个区域都被重新覆盖，但要注意不要留下任何焦黑的痕迹，否则你的努力可能会付诸东流。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/687783ab0019f9f3706073ae29aaddf1.poster.avif?t=1770910965\" width=1170 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/687783ab0019f9f3706073ae29aaddf1.webm?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034650/extras/687783ab0019f9f3706073ae29aaddf1.mp4?t=1770910965\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人游戏或最多4人合作游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >邀请你的朋友一起来玩，2、3 或 4 人一起描绘自然。如果你们能组织好，就能轻松完成皮克画。记住要沟通、观察其他人，最重要的是要协调配合，否则你可能会不小心把皮克画到朋友的皮克上……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你们要齐心协力，按照自己的节奏重建周围的世界，共同平息灼热的岩石。你们有充足的时间，但一旦接近焦土的源头，就必须不惜一切代价抵达。如果分散或撤退太远，你们可能会失去皮库斯，并召唤出恶皮克，这将给你们的旅程增添更多困难。</p>",
